data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, well maintained home boasting a spacious open floor plan and private backyard with no back neighbors. Conveniently located in the heart of Meridian with easy freeway access, near the new Scheels, restaurants and the new shopping center. Spacious bedrooms, huge primary bedroom with walk-in closet and dual vanity. This is an entertainers paradise! Whether spending time with family and friends in the spacious kitchen overlooking the large family room, sitting out back taking in the views, watching the sunset over the mountains or spending time in the loft, there is room for everyone. This is a must see. The low maintenance yard comes with a pergola, extended concrete patio with wrap around sidewalk will give you plenty of room for those summer backyard BBQs. Newer carpets with laundry room upstairs making your daily chores a breeze. Raised garden beds and private walking path are an added bonus. Walking distance from the subdivision park.
